      <section eId="sec_36_71_6">
        <num>36-71-6</num>
        <content>
          <p>Prior to the adoption of an ordinance imposing a development impact fee pursuant to this chapter, the governing body of a municipality or county shall cause two duly noticed public hearings to be held in regard to the proposed ordinance.The second hearing shall be held at least two weeks after the first hearing.</p>
